00:23:07,740 --> 00:23:08,880
Mm...

286
00:23:11,080 --> 00:23:13,970
Can I ask you a question, then?

287
00:23:17,690 --> 00:23:18,440
Mm.

288
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:25,890
How do we let someone we like

289
