369
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:20,180
Can you do me a favor?

370
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:21,920
What favor?

371
00:28:23,360 --> 00:28:24,210
Uh...

372
00:28:25,020 --> 00:28:26,360
Can you help me win Nom Jued's heart?

373
00:28:26,550 --> 00:28:27,270
Huh?!

374
00:28:27,520 --> 00:28:28,760
- Winning Nom Jued's heart?
- Shhh.

375
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:34,020
You know him.

376
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:37,380
So I think you know more about him
than I do.

377
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:39,760
I see...

378
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:42,720
I'll help.

379
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:44,700
I'll give it a shot.

380
00:28:44,840 --> 00:28:45,600
Awesome.

381
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,120
Thank you very much.

382
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:48,410
- I've gotta go now.
- Bye-bye.

383
00:28:51,060 --> 00:28:52,320
Can I be your pupil?

384
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:54,180
Thank you so much, Somchat.

385
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,670
These photos are sublime.

386
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,160
Would you like to see mine?

387
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,470
Please hold this for me.

388
00:29:03,600 --> 00:29:04,600
Let me take some photos.

389
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:13,480
[Phra Aek, The Most Handsome Face]

390
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,200
Phra Aek.

391
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:18,140
Why are you calling me
if you're already next to me?

392
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:21,840
I'm just checking if you've set the picture.

393
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,480
I already have.

394
00:29:24,380 --> 00:29:25,170
Here.

395
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:27,870
Great job, Jued.

396
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:35,780
Do you like my photos?

397
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:40,050
They're alright.

398
00:29:42,010 --> 00:29:46,210
What do I do to make you like them?

399
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,840
Invite me to a shoot next time.

400
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:52,030
If you came with me,

401
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,920
you'd end up taking all the photos yourself.

402
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:57,100
Just try to invite me first.

403
00:29:58,280 --> 00:30:00,500
Who would know that you were free?

404
00:30:00,540 --> 00:30:01,810
I thought you had an exam.

405
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,520
Just call me sometimes.

406
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:06,210
Mm.

407
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:09,360
I guess I'll do that from time to time.

408
00:30:18,920 --> 00:30:19,840
Nom Jued.

409
00:30:20,320 --> 00:30:22,510
Please ask Phra Aek
to give feedback on my work.

410
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:25,380
Oh, sure.

411
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,920
Phra Aek.

412
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:32,170
Please give a comment on Nong Noey's work.

413
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:36,900
Why do I have to do that?

414
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:40,210
Be gentle, okay?

415
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:44,120
Sure, I'll do it.

416
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:54,650
Huh...

417
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,480
Why...

418
00:30:59,120 --> 00:31:00,610
Why do these photos look so familiar?

419
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,000
That's great.

420
00:31:13,640 --> 00:31:14,790
It's conceptual art.

421
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,190
It's also easy to understand.

422
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,710
The fact that you like it is enough for me.

423
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:23,360
When I knew that
the theme of my assignment was time,

424
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:25,520
I was so lost.

425
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,280
After thinking about it,

426
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:30,770
I figured I should make a composite image.

427
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:34,100
That way, the message, "Life is short,

428
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:35,850
so do what you want to do,"
comes through stronger.

429
00:31:36,360 --> 00:31:38,920
I don't know if you can feel it
from the photo, though.

430
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:46,610
Mm.

431
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:48,800
I do now.

432
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,800
I need to go to the bathroom.
I'll be right back.

433
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:54,580
Mm.

434
00:32:15,080 --> 00:32:15,870
Here.

435
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:17,950
Have you been working all night?

436
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:19,440
You're ruining your health.

437
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:22,880
You're kidding me.

438
00:32:23,620 --> 00:32:24,760
I'm still perfectly fine.

439
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:31,440
This is nice, though.

440
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,930
This way, no juniors
would approach me for comments.

441
00:32:34,840 --> 00:32:36,660
You're such a bad senior.

442
00:32:37,090 --> 00:32:37,890
Huh?

443
00:32:38,780 --> 00:32:41,230
Do I actually have what it takes to
comment on their work?

444
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:43,640
Everyone's so passionate that...

445
00:32:44,500 --> 00:32:45,700
I can't.

446
00:33:05,010 --> 00:33:08,730
With this...
What kind of relationship do you want?

447
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:12,920
'Cause...friends don’t do things like this.

448
00:33:16,190 --> 00:33:17,110
We can try.

449
00:33:20,560 --> 00:33:21,550
Try what?

450
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,200
Try becoming a couple?

451
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:26,890
Yeah.

452
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:28,540
Life is short, you know?

453
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,740
It's that simple, see?

454
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,830
Why do you have to make it so complicated?

455
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:39,130
Of course, I have to!

456
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,200
We are friends.

457
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:44,550
One day, if we become more than just friends...

458
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:54,680
See this?

459
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:02,020
Have you ever seen me without this necklace?

460
00:34:04,540 --> 00:34:05,470
I haven't.

461
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:08,520
Since you gave it to me,

462
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,639
I've never taken it off

463
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:13,900
and never will.

464
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:21,370
It's so pretty.

465
00:34:22,570 --> 00:34:24,210
- Thanks!
- Blow out the candles.

466
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:26,000
I forgot that.

467
00:34:33,239 --> 00:34:34,239
- Yay!
- Okay!

468
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:35,800
Happy birthday.

469
00:34:35,840 --> 00:34:37,310
Wish you a ton of happiness,

470
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,730
my first friend.

471
00:34:39,239 --> 00:34:40,780
Sadhu.

472
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:45,070
By the way, why did you gift me the necklace?

473
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:47,290
It's got the letter 'B.'

474
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:48,840
I thought it would suit you well.

475
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:53,560
You know what?

476
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:58,480
Even my partner forgot my birthday.

477
00:34:59,300 --> 00:35:01,910
And my parents...

478
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:05,420
They don’t even get me a cake anymore.

479
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:07,990
It's okay.

480
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:10,360
They'll eventually get it.

481
00:35:11,540 --> 00:35:12,300
Okay?

482
00:35:13,640 --> 00:35:14,790
In this day and age,

483
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:18,440
why can taking nude photos
lead to family estrangement?

484
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:21,440
If I were to do OnlyFans,

485
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,690
