be broken to pieces.

486
00:35:24,760 --> 00:35:26,140
Calm down.

487
00:35:26,520 --> 00:35:28,600
Give them some time
to understand your decision.

488
00:35:29,860 --> 00:35:31,090
Okay?

489
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:38,060
