because of this simple issue, right?

490
00:35:40,240 --> 00:35:42,760
Mm! I will never leave your side.

491
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,800
I promise.

492
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:44,940
Here.

493
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:50,440
Promised.

494
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,370
Let's take things more seriously.

495
00:36:02,040 --> 00:36:03,580
Sorry, I can't keep my eyes open.

496
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,890
You're gonna doze off right here?

497
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,980
Let's go somewhere else.

498
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:12,160
No.

499
00:36:35,680 --> 00:36:36,680
Nom Jued.

500
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:37,960
Are you heading home already?

501
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:39,560
Yes.

502
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,360
I'm heading home.

503
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:44,200
