to wrap things up, right?

504
00:36:44,560 --> 00:36:45,840
I can lend you a hand if you want.

505
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,280
It's fine.

506
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,700
You've done such a great job today.

507
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:50,920
Thanks.

508
00:36:51,340 --> 00:36:55,500
Anyhow, I'd like to
keep learning from you, okay?

509
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:57,640
So...

510
00:36:58,160 --> 00:36:59,440
How are you going home?

511
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:00,520
Do you want me to give you a ride?

512
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:02,160
It's fine.

513
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,440
I'm heading back with my friends.

514
00:37:04,690 --> 00:37:05,690
Mm.

515
00:37:06,240 --> 00:37:08,680
It's better if I give you a ride, though.

