527
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:46,760
Really?

528
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:48,890
I'll come and pick you up, okay?

529
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:50,380
Okay.

530
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,350
Hello?

531
00:37:58,560 --> 00:37:59,520
Are you at the faculty?

532
00:37:59,560 --> 00:38:00,840
Can you come to the club room?

533
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:02,520
I'd like to talk to you about the funding.

534
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,270
Yes, professor.

535
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:07,030
I'm on my way.

536
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:10,630
Nom Jued.

537
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,400
I'm sorry.

538
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:14,330
I'll give you a ride next time.

539
00:38:15,240 --> 00:38:16,630
Oh, really?

540
00:38:18,220 --> 00:38:20,920
That's fine. Next time, okay?

541
00:38:21,200 --> 00:38:21,930
Mm.

542
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:24,330
See you at the cafe tomorrow, okay?

543
00:38:32,160 --> 00:38:34,140
I've had a meeting with the committee

544
00:38:35,160 --> 00:38:37,990
about the Sony World Photography Awards,

545
00:38:39,120 --> 00:38:42,570
and we've discussed that we'll pick
one of your works to exhibit there.

546
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:48,280
Moreover, the chosen candidate will be
100% funded for the photography award,

547
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:50,200
which is either you

548
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:51,560
or you.

549
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:55,910
What do you mean, Professor?

550
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,050
We have to compete against each other?

551
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:01,730
Yes.

552
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,620
Like always.

553
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:06,130
What's the criteria?

554
00:39:07,160 --> 00:39:08,730
If it's past projects,

555
00:39:10,600 --> 00:39:12,200
I guess he deserves the spot.

556
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,450
No, it's much simpler.

557
00:39:15,490 --> 00:39:18,980
It's all up to me.

558
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:23,160
How will you choose one over the other?

559
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:33,260
Both of your final projects
are exhibitions, right?

560
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:35,800
That's the final frontier.

561
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:36,840
It's a fair game.

562
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:39,160
Are you sure that our final projects

