00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,340
He has a point.

565
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:45,530
Yes.

566
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:48,440
But I will not tell you the details.

567
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:50,970
It all depends on your exhibition.

568
00:39:52,650 --> 00:39:53,530
Good luck.

569
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:15,000
Why do I always have to compete against you?

570
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,180
Maybe we're evenly matched.

571
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:22,140
Do you know that

572
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:24,660
I've never wanted to compete against you?

573
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,270
Really?

574
00:40:29,200 --> 00:40:30,090
But I have.

575
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:33,880
Take this as a pity request.

576
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:38,020
You've won in the past.

577
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:39,650
God.

578
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,770
That event wasn't even a big one.

579
00:40:42,240 --> 00:40:43,360
I lucked out.

580
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:45,400
I was chosen because it suited his taste.

581
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:48,160
I'm about to graduate,

582
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:51,650
and finding gigs is already hard as it is.

583
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,480
Unlike you.

584
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,020
You always have gigs coming your way.

585
00:40:59,240 --> 00:41:01,090
You've already bought back your buffalo, too.

586
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:06,080
I fucking hate you.

587
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:09,010
So you're not backing down, huh?

588
00:41:09,680 --> 00:41:10,680
I am not.

589
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:13,680
The same goes for Nom Jued.

590
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:16,950
What about him?

591
00:41:27,240 --> 00:41:29,760
["Good luck on your exam" from Korn]

592
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:42,530
I know that you're hitting on him.

593
00:41:43,880 --> 00:41:45,490
Although I'm not as good-looking as you,

594
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:49,210
I will show him how much I love him.

595
00:41:50,160 --> 00:41:50,940
Fine.

596
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:52,820
I'm hitting on Nom Jued.

597
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:54,960
And I'm very serious about it.

598
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:59,190
Let's make it a fair fight.

599
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:08,500
Bring it.

600
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:09,800
Sure!

601
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:11,320
You're gonna have to deal with me.

602
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,360
We'll see about that.

603
00:42:13,120 --> 00:42:14,220
I'm not backing down.

604
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,180
So am I.

605
00:42:21,560 --> 00:42:22,170
Hey!

606
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,440
We're discussing our project.

607
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:25,690
It's not what you think, Professor.

608
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,100
That's what we're doing, Professor.

609
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:29,210
- Where were we?
- Oh...

610
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,440
It's that topic.

611
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:33,600
It's the photo shoot.

612
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:35,320
- Oh, with that camera?
- Yeah.

613
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,840
Okay, okay. I'll go away now.

614
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:37,880
Good luck.

615
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:08,970
Why is he on my mind?!

616
00:43:23,450 --> 00:43:28,000
[Satrupai: Have you had dinner?]

617
00:43:28,040 --> 00:43:32,520
[Phra Rong: I haven't]

618
00:43:41,560 --> 00:43:45,400
[Satrupai: I'll treat you to one
at the noodle shop, as promised]

619
00:43:45,440 --> 00:43:49,960
[Phra Rong: My class finishes at 10 P.M.]

620
00:43:50,000 --> 00:43:54,360
[Satrupai: That's fine, I don’t mind waiting]

621
00:44:18,080 --> 00:44:19,080
Took you forever.

622
00:44:20,240 --> 00:44:21,350
Every restaurant here is closed.

623
00:44:26,080 --> 00:44:26,950
Hey.

624
00:44:29,280 --> 00:44:30,280
I apologize.

625
00:44:38,520 --> 00:44:39,380
Whatever.

626
00:44:40,020 --> 00:44:41,360
Come to my place.

627
00:45:07,020 --> 00:45:07,920
Good?

628
00:45:23,640 --> 00:45:24,430
Hey.

629
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,580
Just finish it already.

630
00:45:27,080 --> 00:45:28,020
Bugs are everywhere.

631
00:45:30,600 --> 00:45:32,080
You can just go on without me.

632
00:45:34,840 --> 00:45:35,840
No.

633
00:45:36,640 --> 00:45:37,790
It's my plate you're using.

634
00:45:38,360 --> 00:45:40,130
What would I eat food with
if you stole it?

635
00:45:44,360 --> 00:45:45,860
Then...

636
00:45:46,880 --> 00:45:48,420
Let me finish this in your room.

637
00:45:51,320 --> 00:45:52,220
That's so out of line.

638
00:45:52,880 --> 00:45:54,860
We're not that close, you know?

639
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:02,270
Aww, how upsetting.

640
00:46:03,800 --> 00:46:05,360
I even gave you a ride and everything.

641
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:08,280
Yet, we're still not that close?

642
00:46:09,320 --> 00:46:11,160
Let me be clear.

643
00:46:11,520 --> 00:46:14,570
I haven't even brought my friends
to my room.

644
00:46:16,160 --> 00:46:19,290
I only once shared my room
with your fraternity brother.

645
00:46:19,680 --> 00:46:21,340
And who do you think you are
to visit my room?

646
00:46:23,840 --> 00:46:24,700
Really?

647
00:46:26,160 --> 00:46:27,580
You've never taken your partner to your room?

648
00:46:28,200 --> 00:46:30,100
If I had one, I would've done it.

649
00:46:33,800 --> 00:46:34,610
Right.

650
00:46:35,640 --> 00:46:36,640
You have a point

651
00:46:37,160 --> 00:46:38,510
because a few days ago,

652
00:46:39,640 --> 00:46:41,210
you wished for one.

653
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:42,960
Fucking hell.

654
00:46:43,000 --> 00:46:43,980
Just finish it already.

655
00:46:50,800 --> 00:46:51,800
Hey! Hey!

656
00:46:52,200 --> 00:46:53,400
Easy!

657
00:46:57,400 --> 00:46:58,270
Have a drink.

658
00:47:08,880 --> 00:47:11,760
Don't just do everything I say.

659
00:47:16,160 --> 00:47:17,160
I just...

660
00:47:18,320 --> 00:47:19,890
I just don't want you to feel uncomfortable.

661
00:47:22,040 --> 00:47:23,040
I know,

662
00:47:24,800 --> 00:47:30,160
but I'm not used to being treated this much.

663
00:47:31,160 --> 00:47:32,160
Even...

664
00:47:35,720 --> 00:47:39,330
My parents didn't even treat me this well.

665
00:47:41,240 --> 00:47:43,000
So how am I supposed to feel about

666
00:47:43,640 --> 00:47:44,850
you helping me out?

667
00:47:46,720 --> 00:47:47,950
It's fine.

668
00:47:49,080 --> 00:47:50,170
I'm happy to help.

669
00:47:52,040 --> 00:47:53,670
All I want is...

670
00:47:56,300 --> 00:47:57,300
Is?

671
00:47:59,960 --> 00:48:01,850
Let me see you every day.

672
00:48:02,440 --> 00:48:03,400
Okay?

673
00:48:05,520 --> 00:48:07,010
Give me some me-time.

674
00:48:09,160 --> 00:48:10,590
How about this?

675
00:48:11,080 --> 00:48:13,220
I'll text you if you're free.

676
00:48:14,040 --> 00:48:15,380
You have to tell me your availability.

677
00:48:16,480 --> 00:48:17,350
Is that okay?

678
00:48:19,080 --> 00:48:19,970
Fine.

679
00:48:41,560 --> 00:48:43,100
Whoa! A ghost!

680
00:48:43,680 --> 00:48:44,610
Fuck!

681
00:48:46,080 --> 00:48:47,080
It's a ghost!

682
00:48:49,200 --> 00:48:50,200
That's okay.

683
00:48:50,440 --> 00:48:51,750
Ghosts are scary, no?

684
00:48:52,160 --> 00:48:53,770
Why are you scared, Mr. Pai?

685
00:48:54,400 --> 00:48:56,720
I treated my skin like this every day,
and you're still not used to it?

686
00:48:56,760 --> 00:48:58,410
Aww, Mr. Security!

687
00:48:58,880 --> 00:49:00,170
You scared the life out of me.

688
00:49:03,600 --> 00:49:04,960
Okay, I'll be on my way now.

689
00:49:05,000 --> 00:49:06,250
Enjoy yourselves.

690
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:07,440
Enjoy yourselves, okay?

691
00:49:17,640 --> 00:49:19,170
Mr. Pai, have you seen
my bottle of strawberry soda?

692
00:49:19,240 --> 00:49:20,180
It was right there.

693
00:49:20,760 --> 00:49:22,100
I gave it to Rong already.

694
00:49:25,360 --> 00:49:26,300
What about it?

695
00:49:29,640 --> 00:49:30,670
He drank it?

696
00:49:34,640 --> 00:49:36,400
It was for the shrine.

697
00:49:42,520 --> 00:49:43,930
I need to get a new one now.

698
00:49:44,360 --> 00:49:45,660
I gotta go!

699
00:49:46,120 --> 00:49:46,930
Oh...

700
00:49:48,040 --> 00:49:48,960
Shit.

701
00:49:53,040 --> 00:49:54,160
We're in trouble now.

702
00:49:54,760 --> 00:49:55,760
We really are.

703
00:49:56,400 --> 00:49:57,520
Good luck sleeping tonight.

704
00:49:58,240 --> 00:49:59,570
- Better keep your eyes open.
- Ow...

705
00:50:13,920 --> 00:50:15,530
Why is Korn still not here?

706
00:50:19,720 --> 00:50:22,030
Whoa, what's going on, Nom Jued?

707
00:50:22,720 --> 00:50:24,130
Do you need to set it all up yourself?

708
00:50:24,840 --> 00:50:25,840
How strange.

709
00:50:26,480 --> 00:50:28,670
I thought it'd come pre-assembled.

710
00:50:30,600 --> 00:50:32,840
If it's done, please make it quick,

711
00:50:32,880 --> 00:50:34,030
in case there's a customer, okay?

712
00:50:34,600 --> 00:50:35,420
Alright.

713
00:50:55,080 --> 00:50:56,080
Hello, Korn.

714
00:50:56,120 --> 00:50:57,320
Hi, Nom Jued.

715
00:50:57,360 --> 00:50:59,280
I'm working on a project.

716
00:50:59,320 --> 00:51:01,760
I don't think I'll be there in time.

717
00:51:02,440 --> 00:51:05,160
Can you follow the instructions I gave you?

718
00:51:05,960 --> 00:51:07,940
Okay, sure.

719
00:51:13,000 --> 00:51:14,840
It's fine, Korn.

720
00:51:15,840 --> 00:51:17,840
I'll give it a try.

721
00:51:17,880 --> 00:51:18,880
Good luck.

722
00:51:25,080 --> 00:51:26,200
So what is it, Nom Jued?

723
00:51:27,040 --> 00:51:28,040
Are we good to go?

724
00:51:30,160 --> 00:51:30,950
Huh?

725
00:51:32,520 --> 00:51:34,290
Don't look away.

726
00:51:34,600 --> 00:51:35,600
Hurry.

727
00:51:47,480 --> 00:51:48,610
Here I go!

728
00:52:26,440 --> 00:52:27,440
What do I do?

729
00:52:44,360 --> 00:52:45,550
Hello, Phra Aek.

730
00:52:48,120 --> 00:52:49,120
What's up?

731
00:52:49,680 --> 00:52:50,760
Um...

732
00:52:51,920 --> 00:52:53,900
I need your help.

733
00:52:54,120 --> 00:52:58,920
I told the owner of a cafe that
I'd do a promotional shoot for his cafe.

734
00:53:00,080 --> 00:53:02,090
Are you free? Can you come and help me?

735
00:53:04,560 --> 00:53:07,200
Korn is currently busy.

736
00:53:07,960 --> 00:53:13,510
I thought the equipment he gave me
would be pre-assembled.

737
00:53:13,550 --> 00:53:16,140
But that's not the case, Phra Aek.

738
00:53:17,040 --> 00:53:18,520
What am I supposed to do?

739
00:53:21,160 --> 00:53:22,830
Okay, give me a second.

740
00:53:23,200 --> 00:53:25,140
Where's the cafe?
Send me the location.

741
00:53:26,840 --> 00:53:28,080
Thank you so much, Phra Aek.

742
00:53:28,320 --> 00:53:29,840
I'll send it to you right away.

743
00:53:40,960 --> 00:53:41,960
Jued!

744
00:53:44,720 --> 00:53:45,620
Phra Aek!

745
00:54:02,280 --> 00:54:03,410
I wanna look cool.

746
00:54:03,840 --> 00:54:05,150
You, of all people?!

747
00:54:05,400 --> 00:54:06,280
Whoa!

748
00:54:06,320 --> 00:54:07,810
What are you doing, Phra Aek?!

749
00:54:08,260 --> 00:54:09,420
Getting changed, of course.

750
00:54:09,640 --> 00:54:11,270
Do you want me to freeze to death?

751
00:54:11,600 --> 00:54:13,120
If it's still new to you,

752
00:54:15,440 --> 00:54:16,650
would you like to try that again?
